  <title>mongoc_gridfs_get_files()</title>

  <section id="synopsis">
    <title>Synopsis</title>
    <synopsis><code mime="text/x-csrc"><![CDATA[mongoc_collection_t *
mongoc_gridfs_get_files (mongoc_gridfs_t *gridfs);]]></code></synopsis>
  </section>

  <section id="parameters">
    <title>Parameters</title>
    <table>
      <tr><td><p>gridfs</p></td><td><p>A <code xref="mongoc_gridfs_t">mongoc_gridfs_t</code>.</p></td></tr>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section id="description">
    <title>Description</title>
    <p>Retrieves the <code xref="mongoc_collection_t">mongoc_collection_t</code> containing the file metadata for GridFS. This instance is owned by the <code xref="mongoc_gridfs_t">mongoc_gridfs_t</code> and should not be modified or freed.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="return">
    <title>Returns</title>
    <p>Returns a <code xref="mongoc_collection_t">mongoc_collection_t</code> that should not be modified or freed.</p>
  </section>

